          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> the rice and cook for about 5 min or until beginning to turn golden, stirring to coat evenly</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/76.-step5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/76.-step5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/76.-step5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/76.-step5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/76.-step5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">(400ml)</span> of stock to the rice and allow it to absorb, stirring constantly</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the oregano and stir through</p>\r\n<p><strong>Allow</strong> the stock to absorb fully before gradually adding the rest, a ladle at a time</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/76.-step6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/76.-step6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/76.-step6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/76.-step6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/76.-step6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Once</strong> most of the stock has been absorbed and the rice is almost cooked through, add 100g <span class=\"text-danger\">(200g)</span> of cr&egrave;me fra&icirc;che</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the beetroot and cook for another 10 min or until the rice is fully cooked through, stirring constantly</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/76.-step7-x200.jpg",
